#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Now you are ready to play your ﬁrst round of Go. If you are not familiar "
#| "with the rules, we recommend reading the corresponding <ulink url="
#| "\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Go_game\">Wikipedia article</ulink> or "
#| "take <ulink url=\"http://playgo.to/interactive/\">The Interactive Way To "
